    "In a small bowl, mix together lemon juice, garlic, and chopped parsley.",
    "To assemble the bowls, place a cooked fish fillet on the bottom, followed by a scoop of bulghur wheat, chopped tomatoes, and a drizzle of lemon-garlic sauce.",
